name: UFO County
description:
Explore an island with your spaceship to bring back a lot of stuff to your planet

## Rules

> Empty 100% of the map by attracting to you a maximum of objects. The more you catch, the bigger you can get.

> Do it as fast as possible to add your time to the leaderboard

## Screenshots

## Controls

ZQSD (left stick) - Move

Space (triangle / Y) - Dash
